text: Rodica Drăguș (born 28 October 1964) is a Romanian cross-country skier. She competed in three events at the 1988 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian female cross- country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Romania Category:Cross-country skiers at the 1988 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
